Package org.eclipse.mat.query.results

Class TextResult

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mat.query.results.TextResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
IResult
public class TextResult extends Object implements IResult
This result is rendered as text. The input can be plain text, or HTML. Any object addresses can be rendered as links and allow the user to execute queries on the objects.
No Extend:
